Package domain

Class Freelancer

java.lang.Object
domain.Freelancer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Freelancer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Current class represents the tool for creating new collaborators from an organization. This ones may have different roles within their organization (which are listed in the Funcao enum class). Each of them is also described by their name, mobile phone and email.
